title: Neal, Predators drop Lightning in shootout
text: Neal, Predators drop Lightning in shootout OCT 20, 11:20 pm James Neal on his two goals as the Predators beat the Lightning 5-4 in a shootout on Tuesday. He has five goals on the season, all coming in the past three games.
